{"tid":2212593,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《悉尼晨鋒報》：國際政客、人權組織促奧委會撤北京 2022 冬奧主辨權","createTime":"2020-09-22T02:47:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T02:47:56.000Z","uid":48083,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"acf31f23d639ce2783172c006a86ed6da2985c66","tid":2212593,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T02:47:56.000Z","msg":"中國人權狀況繼續成為國際焦點，《悉尼晨鋒報》報道，成員包括英、美、澳、加、日及歐洲多國國會議員的對華政策跨國議會聯盟 (Inter-Parliamentary Alliance on China) 正式向國際奧委會提出重新考慮是否讓中國舉辦 2022 年北京冬奧運。中國外交部暫未回應。<br />\n<br />\n英國議員、對華政策跨國議會聯盟聯合主席 Sir Iain Duncan Smith 表示：「自由國家有一定地位可（對中國）表明，欺壓、威脅、內部鎮壓、邊境爭議、對鄰國態度傲慢，以至破壞香港相關協議，都必然會帶來後果。」「中國現時似乎認為後果只限於（各國的）譴責。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/%E6%82%89%E5%B0%BC%E6%99%A8%E9%8B%92%E5%A0%B1-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E6%94%BF%E5%AE%A2-%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94%E4%BF%83%E5%A5%A7%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83%E6%92%A4%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC-2022-%E5%86%AC%E5%A5%A7%E4%B8%BB%E8%BE%A8%E6%AC%8A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%2582%2589%25E5%25B0%25BC%25E6%2599%25A8%25E9%258B%2592%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25AE%25A2-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E7%25B5%2584%25E7%25B9%2594%25E4%25BF%2583%25E5%25A5%25A7%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2592%25A4%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC-2022-%25E5%2586%25AC%25E5%25A5%25A7%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E8%25BE%25A8%25E6%25AC%258A%2F&d=UI3sabJMorhQDzR%2BXF3zESVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=e52a2e32\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%2582%2589%25E5%25B0%25BC%25E6%2599%25A8%25E9%258B%2592%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25AE%25A2-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E7%25B5%2584%25E7%25B9%2594%25E4%25BF%2583%25E5%25A5%25A7%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2592%25A4%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC-2022-%25E5%2586%25AC%25E5%25A5%25A7%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E8%25BE%25A8%25